name: METAL
description: We are Metal Warrior, the most unique band across the galaxies comprising a whole universe of stories, characters, graphic novels, music, and apparel. We are Warriors who fight, kick, smash, and rock our music across the Time Space Dimension Construct (TSDC)! Our entire raison d’etré is fighting righteous battles and playing metal music together; righting the wrongs of the universe, and celebrating our legendary conquests in song. The Thousand-Year War threw a mighty wrench into our plans. But after surviving that and finally coming back together, our reunion nearly killed us.
